item.title: Pharaoh Necho*, Pharaoh Nechoh*, Pharaoh Neco, Pharaoh Necoh*

body.p: PHARAOH NECHO*, PHARAOH NECHOH*, PHARAOH NECO, PHARAOH NECOH*
Alternate names for Neco, pharaoh of the 26th dynasty (Egypt), who ruled 609–594 BC (2 Kgs 23:29). See Necho, Nechoh, Neco, Necoh.
